body:
WASHINGTON U.S. Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump has a net worth of more than $10 billion and had a 2014 income of $362 million, his press office said in a statement on Wednesday.


 (Reporting by Sandra Maler; Editing by Will Dunham)
description: WASHINGTON (Reuters) - U.S. Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump has a net worth of more than $10 billion and had a 2014 income of $362 million, his press office said in a statement on Wednesday.
title: U.S. presidential candidate Trump has net worth of $10 billion: press office
